-- MOVES-American Century hires Goldman exec as global product head
-- 
-- Mon Aug 11, 2014 11:10AM EDT
-- None



Aug 11 (Reuters) - Investment management firm American Century Investments hired Glen Casey, an executive from Goldman Sachs Asset Management, as senior vice-president and global head of products.

In the newly created role, Casey will lead global product strategy, management and development for all investments. He will report to Chief Marketing Officer Mark Killen.